5:T84a,<p>Discover the iconic Apple iPhone 3G, a device that changed the future of mobile technology with its elegant design and smart functionality. Crafted with a smooth curved body and a premium minimalist finish, the iPhone 3G delivers both style and comfort in your hand.</p><p>Powered by fast 3G connectivity, this smartphone offers improved web browsing, email access, and online experiences compared to earlier mobile devices. Its vibrant touchscreen display provides a smooth and user-friendly interface, making navigation simple and enjoyable for everyday tasks.</p><p>The iPhone 3G combines essential features including music playback, internet browsing, messaging, maps, and access to the revolutionary App Store — allowing users to personalize their phone with a variety of applications and games.</p><p>Designed for people who appreciate simplicity and innovation, the iPhone 3G remains one of the most influential smartphones ever created. Whether for collection, nostalgia, or basic smart functionality, it represents a milestone in modern mobile history.</p><h3>Key Features</h3><ol><li data-list="bullet"><span class="ql-ui" contenteditable="false"></span>Elegant curved and lightweight design</li><li data-list="bullet"><span class="ql-ui" contenteditable="false"></span>Responsive multi-touch display</li><li data-list="bullet"><span class="ql-ui" contenteditable="false"></span>Fast 3G internet connectivity</li><li data-list="bullet"><span class="ql-ui" contenteditable="false"></span>Built-in music and media player</li><li data-list="bullet"><span class="ql-ui" contenteditable="false"></span>Access to apps and mobile games</li><li data-list="bullet"><span class="ql-ui" contenteditable="false"></span>Smooth and intuitive iOS experience</li><li data-list="bullet"><span class="ql-ui" contenteditable="false"></span>Integrated camera for everyday photos</li><li data-list="bullet"><span class="ql-ui" contenteditable="false"></span>Wi-Fi and Bluetooth support</li></ol><p>Per